name: Ma'epe Eresekar?
description:
What are you searching? 


Que procuras?


(*title written in native Tupi language)

A drawing inspired by incursions in the natural landscape of Bonito, in  Pernambuco state - Brazil. This work also part of a series project entitled Estrela Cinnabar.

Mixed media on paper
3966 × 3049 px
